description:
Martial arts expert Tang Lung (Bruce Lee) arrives in Rome to protect a family friend's restaurant from a powerful Mafia man. A violent altercation between Tang and the mobster's heavies persuades the gang boss to call for reinforcements: an American martial arts assassin (Chuck Norris) who challenges Tang to a fight to the death within the walls of the Colosseum.
